### Update Recipe (Protected)
PUT http://localhost:3000/recipes/{{recipeId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Updated Test Recipe",
  "ingredients": ["updated ingredient1", "updated ingredient2"],
  "instructions": "Updated test instructions",
  "prepTime": 15,
  "cookTime": 25,
  "servings": 6,
  "cuisine": "Updated Test",
  "imageUrl": "https://example.com/updated-test.jpg",
  "difficulty": "Medium",
  "tags": ["updated", "test"],
  "author": "Updated Test Author"
}

### Delete Recipe (Protected)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/recipes/{{recipeId}}

